        "action": "Make the period of Ramadan a school holiday",
        "additional_details": "It\u2019s not fair on Muslims. Fasting is a very tiring thing especially as they do it for long periods a day.",
        "background": "The Government should introduce a new school holiday for the entire month of Ramadan. Christmas is a holiday for everyone, including Christians, meaning time off school. But as a Christian, I feel Muslims should get time off too!\r\n\r\n",
